### Get all auctions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auctions

### Get ONE auction
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auctions

### Add new auction
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auctions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "sample!",
    "imgUrl": "https://img.com/s.png"
}

### Check title happy path
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auctions/check-title?title=inny

### Check title - sad path
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auctions/check-title?title=ALLegro